{"tid":25032,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"迎微博1500萬人 42碎老女人濕身開腿送福利","createTime":"2016-12-06T01:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T06:05:01.000Z","uid":25125,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e392237dd9927a1055de484098261348b1dfe36","tid":25032,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:08:48.000Z","msg":"迎微博1500萬人 林志玲濕身開腿送福利<br />\n<br />\n2016年12月02日 14:39&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n黃詩淳／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2016-12-02/656/20161202003810.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2016-12-02%2F656%2F20161202003810.jpg&h=8299ed51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老女人人美心美，是不少人心中女神。(圖／本報系資料照)<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2016-12-02/656/20161202003816.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2016-12-02%2F656%2F20161202003816.jpg&h=44f6e4d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老女人在泳池中倒立伸腿比出1。（圖／翻攝林志玲微博）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2016-12-02/656/20161202003817.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2016-12-02%2F656%2F20161202003817.jpg&h=885ce448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老女人花式謝1500萬人支持。（圖／翻攝林志玲微博）<br />\n<br />\n老女人人美心美，一直是不少人心中女神，日前才剛過完42歲生日，現微博粉絲也突破1500萬，今(2日)早她曬出一段自拍影片，化身水中美人魚送福利，網友大讚她美到沒天理。<br />\n<br />\n為了給1500萬粉絲福利，42碎老女人特地自拍出水芙蓉影片，只見她在水中倒立，用美腿做出「1」，再用手配合做出「5」和「0」，合成「1500」，大方秀出纖長美腿及美胸，不過「神秘三角洲」不小心露出來，她害羞用草莓圖示遮起來，但優美身姿和可愛模樣仍萌翻網友。<br />\n<br />\n她也感性說：「謝謝大家，人生怎麼樣活得精彩，由自己創造。您們給了我動力，也希望這麼多年來，如果我有能夠傳遞一些些的正面能量給與您，就是我存在的理由。」高情商和滿滿正能量，網友都狂讚她是真女神。<br />\n<br />\n(中時電子報)<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20161202003780-260404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20161202003780-260404&d=41Q62glp5DA2hxteu4KnmXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=fb7037e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20161202003780-260404</a>"},{"pid":"bcf10c389bbb2fb81b2a8dfcd5072ee4a886b68b","tid":25032,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:09:31.000Z","msg":"改晒做老女人 成篇文好似恥笑緊佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9257c8c106587620d8be4063c58dd01c2a18ef","tid":25032,"uid":56524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab7e9513a914b4c3f851f0c49a40f34d6d141b5","tid":25032,"uid":694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:11:38.000Z","msg":"碎你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c608a3d15e7217f4eaf2751f318c2f5a42d93431","tid":25032,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi